-- 18th Party Congress Preparation ‘Well Underway,’ China Says
-- B y   B l o o m b e r g   N e w s
-- 2012-09-13T07:22:38Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-09-13/18th-party-congress-preparation-well-underway-china-says.html
Preparations for the Chinese
Communist Party’s 18th Party Congress are well underway and the
date for the gathering will be announced “in due course,”
Foreign Ministry spokesman Hong Lei said in Beijing today.  Asked repeatedly about Vice President  Xi Jinping ’s health,
Hong said he had “answered the question many times” and gave
no details about his condition.  To contact Bloomberg News staff for this story:
